name: Operation Riptide Patch Collection
description: This patch collection contains a variety of embroidered patches commemorating Operation Riptide. Patches can be applied to any agent you own.

name: Stockholm 2021 Legends Sticker Capsule
description:
This capsule contains a single Stockholm 2021 participant High Grade, Holo, Foil, or Gold sticker.

50% of the proceeds from the sale of this capsule support the included organizations.

That sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.
